          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Bureau Research Transparency Act - Amends the Consumer Financial Protection Act of 2010 to require the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB), any time it issues a research paper available to the public, to accompany it with all studies, data, and other analyses on which it was based.</p>]]></text>
